      "source": "berkshire_zh/1984-letter-zh.md",
      "jump_link": "./wiki/letters/1984-letter.md#p32"
    },
    {
      "year": 1985,
      "quote": "在这两个方面，我们的三家企业都经得起考验。",
      "source": "berkshire_zh/1985-letter-zh.md",
      "jump_link": "./wiki/letters/1985-letter.md#p18"
